Interface Input

All Known Subinterfaces:
GraphInput
All Known Implementing Classes:
ByteArrayInput, CodedInput, FilterInput, GraphByteArrayInput, GraphCodedInput, JsonInput, KvpByteArrayInput, KvpInput, XmlInput
public interface Input

An Input lets an application read primitive data types and objects from a source of data.

Author:
David Yu
Date created:
Nov 9, 2009
